{"md5":"a45a2d9197cc4c1545e56eb10533295b","content":"\n\n<p>\n关于编译器和系统的区分老是忘记，故在此记录一下。\n</p>\n\n<!--more-->\n\n\n<p>\n在区分编译器和系统时，都是使用下面这个方式来判断对应宏：\n</p>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//单独区分</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">ifdef</span> xxx</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">elif</span> xxx</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//组合</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (defined(xxx) &amp;&amp; defined(xxx))</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org7f11019\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org7f11019\">区分编译器</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-org7f11019\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org87e7e99\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"org87e7e99\">gcc</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-org87e7e99\">\n<p>\ngcc具有以下宏来标识自己：\n</p>\n<pre class=\"example\">\n__GNUC__\n__GNUC_MINOR__\n__GNUC_PATCHLEVEL__\n</pre>\n<p>\n实际上这些宏都是带有数字的，以表示gcc的版本号。\n</p>\n\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>如果仅仅是判断一个编译器是不是gcc，那么使用以下方式即可</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">ifdef</span> __GNUC__</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>如果对应的代码需要对于gcc不同版本,需要用以下方式</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">define</span> GCC_VERSION (__GNUC__ * <span class=\"number\">10000</span> \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">                     + __GNUC_MINOR__ * <span class=\"number\">100</span> \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">                     + __GNUC_PATCHLEVEL__)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">…</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* Test for GCC &gt; 3.2.0 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> GCC_VERSION &gt; <span class=\"number\">30200</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-orgeb39e3f\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"orgeb39e3f\">Visual C++</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-orgeb39e3f\">\n<p>\nvisual c++ 下判断最常用的就是:\n</p>\n<pre class=\"example\">\n_MSC_FULL_VER\n_MSC_VER \n</pre>\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>如果仅仅是判断一个编译器是不是 visual c++，那么使用以下方式即可</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">ifdef</span> _MSC_VER</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>如果要判断版本则需要以下方式</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//15.00.20706</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> _MSC_FULL_VER &gt; <span class=\"number\">150020706</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//此宏仅包含前两个版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> _MSC_VER &gt; <span class=\"number\">1700</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-org7d882cd\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org7d882cd\">区分系统</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-org7d882cd\">\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-orgb9ebd80\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"orgb9ebd80\">通过CPU字长区分</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-orgb9ebd80\">\n<p>\n在嵌入式开发中，应用代码经常在PC上进行模拟，模拟无误后再在目标板上执行。\n现在PC基本上都是64位了，所以可以通过其字长来判断当前代码是在PC上运行还是在目标机上运行。\n</p>\n\n<div class=\"org-src-container\">\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">if</span> __SIZEOF_POINTER__ == <span class=\"number\">8</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//PC 64bit</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">else</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//target</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"preprocessor\">#<span class=\"keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"outline-container-orgc9b8519\" class=\"outline-3\">\n<h3 id=\"orgc9b8519\">通过系统类型区分</h3>\n<div class=\"outline-text-3\" id=\"text-orgc9b8519\">\n<p>\n不同的系统定义了不同的宏：\n</p>\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>windows \n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>_WIN32</li>\n<li>_WIN64</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li>linux\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li>__linux__</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\nLast Updated 2018-05-27 日 15:22.<br>Render by <a href=\"https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-renderer-org\">hexo-renderer-org</a> with <a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/\">Emacs</a> 25.3.1 (<a href=\"https://orgmode.org\">Org</a> mode 9.1.13)\n"}
